1
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,880
Lu Zhen'an,

2
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,460
I will make your family

3
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,080
pay a hundredfold

4
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,660
for my father's death!

5
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,920
Xia.

6
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,120
Xia?

7
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,000
Uncle Lu.

8
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,360
Dong, you're not a kid anymore.

9
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,340
It's time to think about your future.

10
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,520
I watched you grow up.

11
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,650
Why don't you...

12
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,440
marry me?

13
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,860
Are you insane?

14
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,280
Come on.

15
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,280
Tell Mom you want to marry Su Dong!

16
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,079
Xia.

17
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,720
You should say, "Welcome home, miss."

18
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,760
Welcome home, miss!

19
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,210
Why are you here?

20
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,280
Get out.

21
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,280
Why are you being so hostile?

22
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,290
You haven't changed at all.

23
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:20,120
You get up at 5:00,

24
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,480
go out to exercise,

25
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,450
come back at 6:00 to wash up,

26
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:27,640
and shave at 6:15.

27
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,079
Then you'll have

28
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,079
a cup of sugar‑free Americano

29
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:33,410
and two slices of oat toast for breakfast.

30
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,960
After all these years,

31
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,040
you're still so self‑disciplined.

32
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:39,490
Give it to me.

33
00:03:58,920 --> 00:03:59,640
Brother...

34
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,160
Enough.

35
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,840
Can I still

36
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,920
call you brother?

37
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,320
Lu Fan.

38
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,120
Lu Fan,

39
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:41,920
I'm coming in.

40
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,000
Fan.

41
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,210
Still hungover?

42
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,450
Do you have to do this every year

43
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,240
on your mom's memorial day
to remember her?

44
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,440
None of your business.

45
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,890
Stop pretending to be a loving father.

46
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,320
Fan.

47
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,960
It's been a long time since we sat down

48
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:31,840
and had a proper talk.

49
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:32,770
Talk about what?

50
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:36,159
Men in the Lu family are born heartless.

51
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,000
It runs in our blood, isn't it?

52
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,080
You taught me that.

53
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,850
Don't you remember?

54
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,520
Look at you now.

55
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,760
How could your mom

56
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,600
rest in peace?

57
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,090
Don't you dare mention her!

58
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,520
Cut that pathetic act

59
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,720
and fake sincerity

60
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,240
and get out of my room.

61
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,800
Jian Xi is coming back soon.

62
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,640
It's time for you to get married.

63
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,020
You get out too.

64
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,690
You haven't answered my question,

65
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:32,760
brother.

66
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:39,320
I won't allow any woman
to become the new mistress of this house.

67
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,080
You and your sister failed once,

68
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,340
and you'll fail again.

69
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,840
Tell me,

70
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,880
why did you come back?

71
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,080
Don't forget

72
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,920
what you did to me.

73
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,640
Stop calling me brother.

74
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,680
You don't deserve to.

75
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,560
But

76
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,760
they're getting married soon,

77
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,560
and we'll become family.

78
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,720
And because of that,

79
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:19,160
you'll never get rid of me, brother.

80
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,880
Welcome home, Xia.

81
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,880
By the way, Xia,

82
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,850
your flight was yesterday, right?

83
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,980
Then why did you arrive today?

84
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,159
I went to my father's grave.

85
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,840
I wanted to tell him

86
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:01,160
that my sister has found a good man,

87
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,500
so he can rest in peace.

88
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,640
But the cemetery was closed,

89
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,080
so I couldn't leave until this morning.

90
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,560
Fan,

91
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,880
you also went to the cemetery yesterday,
didn't you?

92
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,880
Who locked Xia in there?

93
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,280
Uncle Lu, it's not like that.

94
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:28,040
I lost track of time

95
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,860
and got locked in by accident.

96
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:32,679
I'm full.

97
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,000
You're lucky you didn't die out there.

98
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:36,799
Lu Fan,

99
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,640
how could you
talk to your sister like that?

100
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,360
Lu Fan!

101
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,320
Calm down.

102
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,140
No need to argue with your son.

103
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,600
Xia, now that you're back,

104
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,530
you should settle down.

105
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,880
We're family.

106
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,860
Isn't it great to live happily together?

107
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,160
Okay, sister.

108
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,360
You're right.

109
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:26,600
Natural beauty is a scarce resource.

110
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,000
Anyone who doesn't use it

111
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,120
to its full potential

112
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,320
is an idiot.

113
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,100
Do you understand?

114
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:44,800
Jian Xi is coming back in three days,

115
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,880
and there'll be a welcome party.

116
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,600
You must outshine everyone

117
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:52,200
and socialize with those

118
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,280
rich heirs,

119
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,200
okay?

120
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,800
Got it.

121
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:03,520
Brother,

122
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,920
wait.

123
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,740
What's wrong with you?

124
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,480
If you want to die, go somewhere else.

125
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,810
Don't die in front of me.

126
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:36,360
Brother, if one day, you watch me die,

127
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,360
will you be sad?

128
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,320
Get off.

129
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,360
Don't be so mean.

130
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:43,580
Just give me a ride.

131
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,300
Can't you use your right hand?

132
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,120
Is it broken?

133
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:17,640
Listen,

134
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,960
I don't have time to play games with you.

135
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,000
Get off now.

136
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,880
I get it now.

137
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,960
Even if I die in front of you,

138
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,780
you won't even shed a tear.

139
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,720
That's right,

140
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:41,160
because you're not worth it.

141
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,200
Because I'm not worth it.

142
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,240
Welcome.

143
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,280
Thanks.

144
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,600
Thanks.

145
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,360
Jian Xi!

146
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,280
Welcome back!

147
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:29,280
Qing, you look so skinny now!

148
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,520
Are you serious?

149
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,500
What's wrong, Jian Xi?

150
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,290
Does your hand hurt?

151
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,440
Just a small gift.

152
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,560
No, please don't!

153
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,200
Jian, please take it.

154
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:12,480
Look at you.

155
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:16,880
Jian, I have a bold suggestion.

156
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:17,720
Go ahead.

157
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,000
Well,

158
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:22,200
they're about the same age.

159
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,960
And before you know it,

160
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,890
they'll grow up.

161
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,840
So, perhaps

162
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,800
they could get engaged.

163
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,480
Jian, listen to me.

164
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:37,480
In this way, we can
take good care of Jian Xi.

165
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,640
More importantly,

166
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:40,100
you have to give us a chance

167
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,000
to pay her back

168
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,440
for saving my son's life.

169
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,560
Okay!

170
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,680
I'm fine. I've taken my medicine.

171
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:53,490
Then you shouldn't drink wine.

172
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,080
Ms. Wu,

173
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,080
you know,

174
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,560
only Ms. Jian

175
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,920
can make him

176
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,960
so nervous.

177
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,680
Exactly.

178
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,640
When are you getting married?

179
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,360
It's up to him.
